ji\" /> <br />\n你班傻鳩都幾撚共產黨<br />\n自己抽水抽撚足半年冇問題好正義，沙拿當時人就唔撚比<br />\n仲要佢原諒拉膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野邏輯，你讀完幼稚園未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後攞出黎講既就唔係怨婦，係抽水叻豬<br />\n我回應返你既就係怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班天才兒童都係開po互含圍威喂，我唔阻你地慢慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c65ae045e719d6e3328b9eed181dc1d87f3fc34","tid":940441,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed2c79024ca0132bb00c149981f94b0fbee296a","tid":940441,"uid":3244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c593e591e8e38d8c3f870bfc1f62ff52785890f1","tid":940441,"uid":163006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"vvd鏟落去個陣唔知有冇對住梅頓斯大叫 you will never walk again呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44185e69433fa866e854c38ee893f884a1e404f6","tid":940441,"uid":165817,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9027cfeba8528485b9797f04406a966b142220c7","tid":940441,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"dbfddf46b9d4376a51f90094b39e82d7938852f6","tid":940441,"uid":165817,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"adba581b52dc71fb5e54c4165ae106be321f05a1","tid":940441,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"半你老味咩，最多咪講到世杯嗰期，之後撚有人講咩<br />\n係你班真怨婦提到依家咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T19:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/SPORT-PREVIEW-Salah-Ramos.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=620&amp;h=413&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2